questions.specification:
Two particles A and B have position vectors:

$$ 
\vec{r}_{A}(t)=\begin{pmatrix}
2 t+1 \\
3
\end{pmatrix}, \quad \vec{r}_{B}(t)=\begin{pmatrix}
5-t \\
1+2 t
\end{pmatrix}
$$

A particle's velocity is given by

$$
\vec{v}(t)=\begin{bmatrix}
2 t \\
3
\end{bmatrix}, \quad \vec{r}(0)=\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
$$
